{"tid":2005984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：3間公司均與今次被政府欽點負責Cu Mask的香港紡織及成衣研發中心有關連 更發現其董事都提名林鄭做特首","createTime":"2020-05-07T12:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T15:55:06.000Z","uid":22556,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9132d1f6da41ecca2eb7a99571c8814e1f3e48c3","tid":2005984,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"翻查資料，3間公司均與今次被政府欽點負責Cu Mask的香港紡織及成衣研發中心（HKRITA）有關連，晶苑集團執行董事王志輝及聯業製衣的副總裁蕭毓然均是HKRITA董事之一，龍達紡織則曾與HKRITA合作紡織項目。<br />\n<br />\n證實是政府口罩生產商後，晶苑國際（上市編號：2212）股價今日曾飆逾15%，收市報2.25元，市值單日增加7.13億元。<br />\n<br />\n2017年特首選舉中，該界別的17名選委有14人都提名了林鄭月娥，其中梁嘉彥、馮煒堯、黃啟智現時都是HKRITA的董事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200507&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60913478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200507%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60913478&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdU9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=45155bc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200507%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60913478&h=2104a2b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200507&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60913478</a>"},{"pid":"9bdf385806d0142cfef2ab59c68fe467e0b73e79","tid":2005984,"uid":106321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾自己咪又係到搞<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">藍色經濟圈</span>"},{"pid":"2d01c24f1ea16f915c3e0a55b65056f929e42680","tid":2005984,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb0d64bdc9a4115cd04e34d75e469cd83e2cf9d","tid":2005984,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:05:42.000Z","msg":"然後可以做d咩？"},{"pid":"e6c965e712ffca87c828e4f5115eed6e7377cd02","tid":2005984,"uid":22556,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9bdf385806d0142cfef2ab59c68fe467e0b73e79","tid":2005984,"uid":106321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾自己咪又係到搞<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">藍色經濟圈</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:06:41.000Z","msg":"唔係 係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">官商勾結<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dbb046a649fc8617117613c321848321308dfc4e","tid":2005984,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XO3xkqD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXO3xkqD.png&h=e2d29eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eebc11cefe22e28ef45023c8188a880936a5dd6","tid":2005984,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bb0d64bdc9a4115cd04e34d75e469cd83e2cf9d","tid":2005984,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:05:42.000Z","msg":"然後可以做d咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"我諗過埋聽日 D 議員應該會做野掛"},{"pid":"02c053dfeb604fbc03dc41a5aff2dc1a383c2e1c","tid":2005984,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"識啱人一向都好重要"},{"pid":"2fc642e97dbcf27a38d97715b55138aa5f6df615","tid":2005984,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWgyPB3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWgyPB3.jpg&h=a87d6da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府宣布向全民派發可重用的「銅芯抗疫口罩」，但因沒有公開招標及一度隱瞞生產商，被質疑有利益輸送之嫌。 本網記者翻查資料，發現晶苑國際、聯業製衣及龍達紡織都與獲政府欽點，研發口罩的香港紡織及成衣研發中心（HKRITA）有關。HKRITA 最少兩名董事，曾在 2017 年特首選舉中提名林鄭月娥做特首&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n報道：<a href=\